<item>
            <title>[BCEL-110] Problem with JAXB if the bcel classloader is used</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/BCEL-110</link>
                <project id="12314220" key="BCEL">Commons BCEL</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When I try to run program with a JAXB code I got an exception if the bcel&lt;br/&gt;
